## Development Workflow

This project follows **Specs-Driven Development (SDD)**. All implementation
must be preceded by spec reviews from the following roles, executed via
Goose recipes:

{% if roles %}
{% for role in roles %}
{{ loop.index }}. **{{ role.title }}** — `{{ role.recipe }}`
   _{{ role.purpose }}_
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
1. **Architect** — `recipes/architect.yaml`
   _Define system structure, tech stack, and data flow_
2. **UI/UX Designer** — `recipes/ui-designer.yaml`
   _Define CLI commands, config, env vars, and error messages_
3. **Interface Designer** — `recipes/interface-designer.yaml`
   _Define APIs, file formats, and integration contracts_
4. **Security Analyst** — `recipes/security-analyst.yaml`
   _Threat model, input validation, and access controls_
5. **Edge Case Analyst** — `recipes/edge-case-analyst.yaml`
   _Boundary conditions, failure modes, and test scenarios_
6. **Senior Developer** — `recipes/senior-developer.yaml`
   _KISS review, task breakdown, and testing strategy_
{% endif %}

**Rule:** No code is written before all six roles have reviewed the specs.

